需求:
1. 色温检测: Color Temperature Testing
2. Emax检测: Emax Testing
3. 黑白对比度: Black and White Contrast
4. 照度均匀性: Illuminance Uniformity
5. 色度均匀性: Chromaticity Uniformity
6. FOV检测: Field of View Testing
7. 光学畸变检测: Optical Distortion Testing
8. MTF检测: Modulation Transfer Function Testing
9. 色差检测: Chromatic Aberration Testing
10. 光通量检测: Luminous Flux Testing
11. 解像力测量: Resolution Measurement
12. 缺陷点检测: Defect Detection
13. 视场外杂散光检测: Stray Light Testing